column5: I am heading up to Gullrock for my first visit there this weekend. Is there somewhere I can get a lake topo map of any kind? Thx.

Zim, They will have good quality maps of Gullrock at camp. I believe they are less than $5 to buy and I would recommend that you buy one when you arrive. Gullrock is not that large but it is nice to have something to refer to if you get direction turned. Well, 3 more sleepless night until I can smell that fresh Canadian air and "fish on"!!!! :-) Renn
